RTAPI-Demo

To use insert your AuthToken to the  RTAPIDemo.py on line 20
authToken="put your auth Token here"

MAC address of incoming messages are always displayed


Streaming Realtime API usage: python3 RTAPIDemo.py [-h] [-r] [-e] [-s] [-rid] [-rp] [-p] [-d] [-v] [-i INPUT] [-o OUTPUT]

optional arguments: -h, --help show this help message and exit -r, --raw display raw data. -e, --epoch Display EPOCH Time. -m, --mac Display MAC. -s, --sequencenumber Display sequence number. -rid, --recieverid Display Reciever ID. -rp, --recieverplatform Display Reciever Platform(RDK version). -p, --pipe Display pipe. -d, --description Display description. -v, --verbose Verbose mode (output everything) -i INPUT, --input INPUT Subnet (in quotes" ".) 
examples: To recieve all messages from a single Subnet -i="<Your Subnet>" To recieve all messages from a Subnet (single warehouse) -i=:"<your Subnet>"

-o OUTPUT, --output OUTPUT Your log file (in quotes" "). NOTE you will need a sub directory named "logs/"

example: To recieve all messages from a single Subnet output MAC Pipe Sequence number and description log to logs/My.log

    python3 RTAPIDemo.py -p -s -d -i="<your Subnet>" -o="My.log"
